      "date_checked": "2026-05-01",
      "supports": "Computer-use systems need a loop that proposes actions, executes them in an environment, captures state, handles safety checks, and should be run in sandboxed environments with allowlists and oversight"
    },
    {
      "source": "OpenAI Safety Checks",
      "url": "https://developers.openai.com/api/docs/guides/safety-checks",
      "date_checked": "2026-05-01",
      "supports": "Computer-use and agent actions need safety-check handling, oversight, acknowledgement, and policy-aware blocking before risky actions proceed"
    },
    {
      "source": "OpenAI Safety Best Practices",
      "url": "https://developers.openai.com/api/docs/guides/safety-best-practices",
      "date_checked": "2026-05-01",
      "supports": "Production AI applications should layer safety controls, monitoring, escalation, and policy compliance around model outputs and tool actions"
    },
    {
      "source": "OWASP Agentic Security Initiative",
      "url": "https://genai.owasp.org/initiatives/agentic-security-initiative/",
      "date_checked": "2026-05-01",
